#
# Purpose: Project-specific overrides for go-bt
# Load Order: 90 (loaded after all defaults, overrides any earlier settings)
#
# This file contains project-specific configuration that overrides defaults from:
# - 00-core.env (core settings)
# - 10-coverage.env (coverage defaults)
# - 10-security.env (security defaults)
#
